263:  implementation "com.typesafe.akka:akka-stream_${versions.ScalaBinary}:${versions.AkkaVersion}"
402:<p>Default marshallers are provided for simple objects like String or ByteString, and you can define your own for example for JSON. An additional module provides JSON serialization using the spray-json library (see <a href="common/json-support.html">JSON Support</a> for details):</p><dl class="dependency"><dt>sbt</dt><dd><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-scala">val AkkaHttpVersion = "10.5.3"
